## 3. GOD FILE main.go: Как организовать HTTP роутинг

### АНТИПАТТЕРН (main.go — 1810 строк, SQL внутри хендлеров):
```go
// ПЛОХО: main.go
router.GET("/api/v1/timeseries/historical", func(c *gin.Context) {
    uuid := c.Query("uuid")
    // ... 50 строк парсинга параметров
    rows, err := db.Query(`
        SELECT time_bucket($1, time) AS bucket, AVG(i1)...
        FROM me337_timeseries
        WHERE device_uuid = $2 AND time >= $3
    `, bucket, uuid, from)
    // ... 30 строк маршалинга результата
    c.JSON(200, result)
})
// И так 50 раз
```

### ПРАВИЛЬНО: Тонкие хендлеры + сервисный слой
```go
// cmd/energy-monitor/main.go — ТОЛЬКО bootstrap (~100-150 строк)
func main() {
    cfg := config.MustLoad("config.json")
    logger := logger.New(cfg.LogLevel)
    db := postgres.MustConnect(cfg.Postgres)
    defer db.Close()

    // Repositories
    deviceRepo := repo.NewDeviceRepo(db)
    tsRepo := repo.NewTimeseriesRepo(db)
    econRepo := repo.NewEconomicsRepo(db)

    // Services (Dependency Injection через конструкторы)
    alertSvc := app.NewAlertService(logger)
    broadcaster := websocket.NewBroadcaster()
    telemetrySvc := app.NewTelemetryService(tsRepo, alertSvc, broadcaster, logger)
    deviceSvc := app.NewDeviceService(deviceRepo, mqttClient, logger)
    econSvc := app.NewEconomicsService(econRepo, logger)

    // HTTP
    router := httpAdapter.NewRouter(cfg, telemetrySvc, deviceSvc, econSvc, logger)
    
    // Start
    srv := &http.Server{Addr: cfg.HTTPAddr, Handler: router}
    go srv.ListenAndServe()

    // Graceful shutdown
    quit := make(chan os.Signal, 1)
    signal.Notify(quit, syscall.SIGINT, syscall.SIGTERM)
    <-quit
    srv.Shutdown(context.Background())
}

// internal/adapter/http/router.go
func NewRouter(cfg *config.Config, ts *app.TelemetryService, ds *app.DeviceService, es *app.EconomicsService, logger *slog.Logger) *gin.Engine {
    r := gin.New()
    r.Use(LoggingMiddleware(logger), RecoveryMiddleware(), CORSMiddleware())

    api := r.Group("/api/v1")
    {
        RegisterDeviceRoutes(api, ds)
        RegisterTimeseriesRoutes(api, ts)
        RegisterEconomicsRoutes(api, es)
        RegisterAuthRoutes(api, cfg)
    }
    return r
}

// internal/adapter/http/timeseries_handler.go — ТОНКИЙ хендлер
type TimeseriesHandler struct {
    svc    *app.TelemetryService
    logger *slog.Logger
}

func RegisterTimeseriesRoutes(rg *gin.RouterGroup, svc *app.TelemetryService) {
    h := &TimeseriesHandler{svc: svc}
    rg.GET("/timeseries/historical", h.GetHistorical)
    rg.GET("/timeseries/realtime", h.GetRealtime)
}

func (h *TimeseriesHandler) GetHistorical(c *gin.Context) {
    // 1. Parse & validate request (5-10 строк)
    req, err := parseHistoricalRequest(c)
    if err != nil {
        c.JSON(400, gin.H{"error": err.Error()})
        return
    }
    // 2. Call service (1 строка)
    result, err := h.svc.GetHistorical(c.Request.Context(), req)
    if err != nil {
        c.JSON(500, gin.H{"error": "internal error"})
        h.logger.Error("GetHistorical failed", "err", err)
        return
    }
    // 3. Respond (1 строка)
    c.JSON(200, result)
}
```

### ПРАВИЛО: HTTP хендлер = Parse request → Call service → Send response. Максимум 20-30 строк.
Если в хендлере есть SQL, if/else бизнес-логика, или больше 30 строк — рефакторить.

